snippet.title: Super Mario Construct V8: Boom Boom Sneak Peek!
snippet.description:
Heya all, work on the next snapshot is wrapping up - we've got a few more new features yet to uncover, too! In this video, you'll see the revamped Boom Boom, which much like almost anything in V8, behaves a bit differently from his V7 counterpart - thanks to many tweaks and adjustments!

Here is a sneak peek of what you can expect to come.

Join the SMC server here if you're interested: https://discord.gg/NXjVVmT
